Message.message: Argh! Why are there so many people here this early in the morning! GET OUTTA MY WAY!
I don't have the time to wait in these lines right now. CAN'T THESE PEOPLE GO ANY FASTER?
Ooh, the moving walkways, this should hopfully "move things along"!
Finally, my gate! And there's even a seat for me!
"You didn't hear? The flight got delayed for four hours!"
The wedding starts in three hours! I'll never make it by car!
Wait a second, why are all these people still sitting at the gate if I was nearly late?
I'm going to be late for my flight!
